Thanks April, but I am aware of the shortcomings of the box, and all these methods. I don&#39;t really need some &quot;expert&quot; telling me what it really is. I&#39;ve said very often that none of this s--- it written stone, and it ain&#39;t gospel either, same with these opinions. 

 Personally I don&#39;t give a crap about proof, it&#39;s the fact that something talks that intrigues me, and how to make it better. These skepdicks make alot of assumptions about my motives, and character. 99% of the time they are way wrong. I don&#39;t do this work for mankind, or the paranormal community, fame or fortune. That&#39;s why the skeptic attacks are so insulting and infuriating. 


Frank-S

